Config server should be able to return which ad experience is enabled within SIA alongside the SIA enabled flag

Example

```
{
samsunginteractivead: "on",
  sia_experiences: {
    clicktoemail: "on",
    productcarousel: "on",
    pasueads: "on"
  }
}
```

